A simple dice rolling bot made as an excercise to learn botbuilder-js
Bot is built with the assumption you are in direct chat with it and expect a response to every input, as opposed to listening to a channel.


setup
npm install

commands
will detect 'roll xdy' in any command as well as whenever 'roll' is used.
If 'roll' is used, it will prompt the user for an amount of dice as well the value of those dice.
